OL,5, Race should be made a central part of  
OL,6, the UK's independent public inquiry    
OL,7, into the pandemic, campaigners say.    
OL,9,FA letter seen by BBC News, sent to the 
OL,10,Fchairwoman of the Covid-19 inquiry,    
OL,11,Fcalls for it to look at "racism as a   
OL,12,Fkey issue" at every stage.             
OL,14,FEthnic minorities were significantly   
OL,15,Fmore likely to die with Covid-19,      
OL,16,Faccording to official figures.         
OL,18,FAn inquiry spokesperson said the       
OL,19,Funequal impacts of the pandemic would  
OL,20,Fbe at the forefront of its work.       
